snippet.title: Teared - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2782490?utm_source=youtube

Embark on a thrilling 3D arcade action-platformer adventure in Teared! Travel through 9 challenging levels filled with epic bosses and a variety of deadly creatures. Are you ready for this epic journey?

Features:

- 9 challenging levels and 2 bonus stages to conquer.
- Face off against 9 epic bosses with unique abilities and attack patterns.
- Battle a diverse range of enemies, including dragons, skeletons, bats, spiders, cyclops, and more.
- 3 different weapons available.
- A side-scroller game with 3D graphics.
